08/05/2007
SOFIA, Bulgaria -- Counterterrorism forces acting on intelligence information have prevented a bomb plot, according to an announcement Monday (May 7th).
Three people, all with long criminal records, were detained before dawn Sunday during raids on their homes.
Officials say a significant amount of explosives, weapons and other items were seized.
Still unclear is the target of the plot.
(bTV, Darik, BNR, Mediapool - 07/05/07)
